                    "stepText": "Now, using the ideal gas law, we need to compute the numerator of the expression $!$nRT$!$. Calculate $!$n \\times R \\times T$!$ using $!$n=10$!$, $!$R=8.314\\,J/(mol\\cdot K)$!$, and the converted final temperature from the previous step. What is the product? (Round to one decimal place)",
